title: Beyond the Clouds
subTitle: Tara inadvertently sets the wheels in motion for a life-altering, unsavoury occurrence after she seeks help from the wrong person to protect her drug-dealing brother from the police.

title: Sherdil: The Pilibhit Saga
subTitle: A sacrificed village leader, Gangaram, embarks on a journey in search of a dangerous tiger that threatens people.

title: Kadvi Hawa
subTitle: A blind old man, worried about the survival and well-being of his son, decides to strike a deal with a debt collector to prevent his child from falling into a debt trap.

title: Mere Pyare Prime Minister
subTitle: After his mother is raped one night, Kannu, an eight-year-old boy, writes a letter to the prime minister of India and embarks on a journey from Mumbai to Delhi with his two friends.

title: U-Turn
subTitle: A journalist investigating traffic offenders on a flyover becomes embroiled in an investigation after being accused of murdering one of the motorcyclists.

title: Sarkar 3
subTitle: Determined to protect public interest and his own authority, Sarkar finds himself locked in a cat-and-mouse game with his adversaries, both external and internal.

title: Baar Baar Dekho
subTitle: Mathematics professor Jai gets cold feet about marrying his girlfriend Diya. After the marriage is cancelled, he goes on a journey through time, seeing what it would be like if he married Diya.

title: Jersey
subTitle: Arjun, a talented but failed cricketer, decides to return to cricket in his late thirties driven by the desire to represent the Indian cricket team and fulfil his son's wish for a jersey as a gift.

title: Badla
subTitle: Naina, a successful entrepreneur, gets caught in a web of accusations when her lover is found dead. Later, she hires a reputable lawyer to work with her on the case.

title: Swatantra Veer Savarkar
subTitle: After witnessing the tyranny of Britishers at a very young age, Vinayak Damodar Savarkar joins the struggle for India's freedom and faces severe incidents in his life.

title: Murder Mubarak
subTitle: When a murder occurs at an elite club in Delhi, an eccentric police officer investigates the case. As time passes, suspicion falls on the club's wealthy guests.

title: Agent Vinod
subTitle: On a mission to decipher a colleague's dying message, RAW agent Vinod travels across different countries and uncovers a dangerous conspiracy against India.

title: Agent Vinod
subTitle: On a mission to decipher a colleague's dying message, RAW agent Vinod travels across different countries and uncovers a dangerous conspiracy against India.

title: Buddha in a Traffic Jam
subTitle: A management student's social media success unexpectedly pulls him into a dangerous clash of idealogies, where trust breaks down and agendas collide within academic walls.

title: Turtle
subTitle: Ramkaran tirelessly churns the dry earth of a village in Rajasthan for water. Meanwhile, the villagers participate in desperate measures to satisfy their thirst.

title: Kites
subTitle: Jay, a dance instructor, falls in love with Tony's fiancee. They make their daring escape and get married, but Tony is determined to track them down.

title: Akaash Vani
subTitle: During their time in college, Akaash and Vani fall for each other. But when Akaash moves to the UK for further studies, unforseen circumstances force Vani to marry Ravi, an abusive man.

title: Badhaai Do
subTitle: After being pestered to get married, a closeted gay cop decides to enter a marriage of convenience with a lesbian woman to appease his family.

title: Dil Juunglee
subTitle: Love blossoms between Koroli and Sumit, two people with contrasting personalities, when the latter joins her English class.

title: Satyaprem Ki Katha
subTitle: Satyaprem tries hard to prove himself as a worthy person and restore the faith in the love of Khata, who is overwhelmed by her breakup.

title: Naam Shabana
subTitle: Shabhana, desperate for justice, agrees to join a secret intelligence agency in exchange for their help in unmasking her friend's murderer.

title: Goodbye
subTitle: A family crumbles when the mother suddenly passes away and the children try to rush home to complete her final rites. However, differing opinions cause clashes among the clan.

title: The Kerala Story
subTitle: Shalini, a former nursing student from Kerala, who later becomes the wife of a terrorist, testifies her life story and her journey from being a naive girl to another victim of terrorism.

title: Mission Majnu
subTitle: An undercover Indian spy takes on a deadly mission to expose a covert nuclear weapons program in the heart of Pakistan that could destroy the free world.

title: Mission Majnu
subTitle: An undercover Indian spy takes on a deadly mission to expose a covert nuclear weapons program in the heart of Pakistan that could destroy the free world.

title: The Last Color
subTitle: Choti, a young tightrope walker, wishes to pursue her education but struggles to make a living. She soon befriends Noor, a widow who yearns to play Holi but is forced to live a life of abstinence.

title: Holiday
subTitle: Muskaan, an unpopular, shy girl, falls for Dino, a charismatic dancer, while on a vacation in Goa with her family. However, things become complicated when her father objects to their relationship.

title: Sniff
subTitle: Sunny, who lacks the sense of smell, finds his olfactory abilities enhanced after becoming a victim of a laboratory accident, which turns him into a superhero.

title: Footfairy
subTitle: A CBI officer investigates a string of gruesome murders committed by a serial killer with a foot festish. However, things take an ugly turn when he gets close to catching the killer.

title: Udta Punjab
subTitle: A rock star, a migrant labourer, a doctor and a policeman find themselves struggling to cope with the ensuing chaos surrounding a drug crisis in Punjab, India.

title: Zero
subTitle: A vertically-challenged bachelor with a larger-than-life personality discovers his life's purpose through his relationships with two wildly different women.

title: The Kashmir Files
subTitle: A young college student sets out to uncover the truth behind his parents' brutal killings in Kashmir, leading him to a web of lies and conspiracies.

title: Gaami
subTitle: Shankar, a reclusive man, embarks on an adventure to the Himalayas to find a cure for a rare human condition. However, things get complicated when his past unfolds.

title: Don 2
subTitle: Trouble awaits Don as the European drug cartel bosses plan his downfall. However, new allies and former foes promise to aid him in the challenging times.

title: Farrey
subTitle: Brought up in an orphanage, child prodigy Niyati gets admitted into a prestigious school. Soon, surrounded by money, she gets engulfed in a cheating racket.

title: Happy Bhag Jayegi
subTitle: Happy, a vibrant Indian girl, elopes on the day of her wedding so that she can marry Guddu, the man she loves. However, she mistakenly arrives at the home of a Pakistani politician where chaos ensues.
